        ax.set_title(f'   {col}', fontsize=14)

        ax.set_ylabel(' ')

        ax.set_ylabel(' ')

#  ,      
def group(feature):
    if feature <= 500:
        f = 'Score before 500'
    elif feature > 500 and feature <= 700:
        f = 'Score 500-700'
    else:
        f = 'Score after 700'
    return f
#   apply         
bank['score_group'] = bank['score'].apply(group)

def group(feature):
    if feature <= 30:
        f = 'age before 30'
    elif feature > 30 and feature <= 40:
        f = 'age 30-40'
    elif feature > 40 and feature <= 50:
        f = 'age 40-50'
    else:
        f = 'age after 50'
    return f

#  ,     balance
def group(feature):
    if feature <= 50000:
        f = 'balance before 50 t.r.'
    elif feature > 50000 and feature <= 100000:
        f = 'balance 50-100 t.r.'
    elif feature > 100000 and feature <= 150000:
        f = 'balance 100-150 t.r.'
    elif feature > 150000:
        f = 'balance after 150 t.r.'   
    else:
        f = 'balance empty'
    return f
